Subject: RE: [T2] Exhaust system bolts

> Does anyone know where I can buy bolts that would stand up to the
temperatures of the exhaust system?

Lowes and Home Depot both have specialty sections that include both Grade 5
and Grade 8 bolts, washers and nuts.  Bought both on several occasions and
have not had problems with stripping the threads.  I believe that the Grade
8 are graded for automotive applications.

- Mike
